  m_text: 'i HAVE DIED.....

    Thanks to me being an elf, i managed to survive.
    Although just as a lowly vine.


    I never imagined, that I, a noble dignified
    elf, would have to climb on the walls of a dirty cave.


    THankfully there
    should be an



    Nearby.


    EVEN if i am limited by nutrients in the soil,




    and
    return to my noble life....


    WISH ME LUCK.....'
